snippet.title: M.U.L.E. C64 -- Longplay with YARG!
snippet.description: M.U.L.E. longplay on the C64, introductory round (6 months).  This is the longplay of me doing MULE for the Commdore 64.  I have a review video available on my primary channel that you should check out as well.
